prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon watercolor of a slightly frazzled, party-hat-wearing snail enthusiastically trying to blow out a single, very stubborn birthday candle on a tiny cupcake, the flame comically leaning away from the snail's puff of air. The snail has a determined but silly expression. The background is a soft, simple wash of pastel colors. Centered above the scene, the word "birthday" is written in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script. The entire image is a flat 2D artwork in a watercolor painting style, with soft flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds at the edges of the figures.
